ue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9td","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36404,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-al-duha-enough\/","url_meta":{"origin":36407,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Salat al-Duha, Allah will be enough","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Nu\u2019aym ibn Hammar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty says: O son of Adam, do not be frustrated to perform four cycles of prayer for me at the beginning of your day. I will suffice you for the rest of it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5514,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/25\/virtue-salat-first-row-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36407,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Virtue of praying in first row of congregation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubay ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the first row of prayer resembles the rows of angels. If you knew its virtue, you would compete for it. The prayer of a man with another man is more purifying than his prayer\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31747,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/in-salat-waiting-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":36407,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: You are in prayer if you are waiting for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: We prayed with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, at nightfall and he did not come out until half of the night had passed. The Prophet said, \u201cTake your places.\u201d We took our places and the Prophet said, \u201cVerily, people have prayed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36424,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/sunan-maghrib-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":36407,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayer between Maghrib and Isha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: In regards to the verse, \u201cThey arise from their beds, calling upon their Lord in fear and in hope, spending from what We have provided them,\u201d (32:16). Anas said, \u201cThey are those who are awake to pray between sunset and evening prayer.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5660,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/supplication-in-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":36407,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet\u2019s suppli